                  <br /><span class="cell-head">Zeemerix PlayByPlay Baseball -- for iPhone and iPad</span>

                  <br />Major League Baseball simulation game for iPad and iPad Pro.
                  <br />Zeemerix PlayByPlay Baseball lets you set the lineups and choose the starting pitchers.
                  You can choose when to pinch it, pinch run, change pitchers, and call special
